# IDEA 激活插件收集
## 1 jetbra破解

[下载地址](https://gh.con.sh/https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/releases/download/V1.0.1/jetbra2099.zip)

### 1.1 打开下载好的jetbra解压并打开scripts

![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/e5d45b35-c914-40ea-a3f8-02741cbbab66)

### 1.2 双击运行uninstall-all-users.vbs,然后点确定
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/98afac01-c55f-4931-b8c8-77b86bc15895)

### 1.3 安装成功
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/9f9492a6-99dc-4f47-bf25-6748c8f69e32)
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/1802c0de-9d0a-4df0-b4df-de7fe170b72f)
> 两个弹窗都一定要弹，不弹就失败
### 1.4  再运行install-all-users.vbs
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/19270aa9-e19b-4da6-84ce-b3531a1006d4)
> 跟上面同理。也是需要等两个框
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/599d2950-d73b-4fce-aa2b-1fb070c88b4f)
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/207f5345-02f7-4783-a8af-3a97c618127e)

### 1.5 开始激活
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/d63ee6ff-a4e9-4ca4-889b-bedc1ef905e9)
再打开IDEA，输入激活码，activate即可
```text
X9MQ8ML8U7---
```
### 1.6 激活成功
![image](https://github.com/jadehh/idea_activate/assets/20532462/2929996b-8cba-4bc2-9cef-d8d5703be098)
